parameters:
Cerburus Octopus: Hmm, the sales for the "Memimi Sex Rights
at Shark Mountain" are surprisingly poor... Feels like we're
not even selling 10 a day...

Henchman: Maybe the price is set too high? I mean, for such
a beauty, it's a bargain, but you can't shake down an empty
sleeve, right?

Henchman: Times are tough... I wanted to buy one too, but
all my savings combined, I only have 4000 yen.

Memimi: (Just one person buying it is already an
immeasurable mental damage to me! Being forced to perform
fellatio hundreds of times a day, and then having to go all
the way... It's unbearable!!)

Memimi: I can't deal with this anymore!! It's time for a
rematch, Cerburus Octopus!! I'll defeat you, take back the
organization, and protect myself!!

Cerburus Octopus: Oh my, I didn't expect you still had the
will to challenge me again... Have you forgotten the huge
commotion from last time?

Henchman: Gahaha, don't talk about things you can't do! No
one can pull off such a stunt twice or thrice!

The conditions for a monster fight rematch... The victor
must complete any one task set by the other... Last time,
Memimi was forced to do something outrageous during a live
national broadcast—reverse raping a celebrity.

As a result of exposing her lewd behavior on TV, she became
internet news, was featured in sports newspapers, and became
the talk of the town... The amount of trouble Memimi went
through to clean up after, how embarrassed and distressed
she was...

Memimi: (I'd never do such a thing again...! It's
traumatic... such a... But, I have no choice but to do it...
Besides, TV is already...)

Memimi: That was nothing at all! As if an experienced girl
like me would break down just because I did it on national
live broadcast! Just state your conditions already!

Memimi: Ah, but let me make it clear, TV is off-limits
now... Bunny-chan mentioned that there were serious
complaints from all sides, and even the stations are on
guard now!

Cerburus Octopus: Tch, looks like hijacking the program
multiple times is out of the question... So who should we
have her reverse rape this time... Hmm...

Memimi: (Is reverse raping someone a given now...? I don't
want to... I really don't want to...)

Henchman: Speaking of which, I'm an alumnus of Doritoku
Academy... There's this really intense creepy otaku in the
manga club... Probably a third-year by now...

Cerburus Octopus: Oh, that's it!! I've decided... "Reverse
rape the manga club's creepy otaku during a whole school
assembly while making out with him"!!
"No matter what happens, don't give up! The\nCerberus Octopus Rematch Story!"
"Let's go to the Monster Fight arena!"

Memimi: (If I rush into battle now, I'll just lose again...
There are quite strict conditions for a rematch, I don't
want to waste this chance... Maybe I should wait for the
right moment...)
